{"tid":2026421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【認真】唔改變現時抗爭模式　捐幾多錢比612基金都冇用（利申：已捐）","createTime":"2020-05-21T02:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:49:31.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80eb72fbe6ebfd8bee2e1cc0270f1362556c594b","tid":2026421,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:51:40.000Z","msg":"首先，我已經出左分力，所以想講兩句。<br />\n<br />\nProof:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKXzTps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKXzTps.jpg&h=944a4fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n612基金成立左差唔多一年，全香港大大話話捐左億幾兩億<br />\n<br />\n問題係，大部份款項都用係訴訟、保譯、律師費<br />\n<br />\n保譯金下下6位數，即是說，<strong>你同我既捐款，大部份最終入左港共口袋</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係話當手足condom，唔係話唔捐，但再咁落去捐幾多億都冇用，結果都係養肥港共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢億幾兩億，點解要咁樣浪費？"},{"pid":"3eff017524141893a142e8b955e3ef9cf6f887b8","tid":2026421,"uid":358760,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c6a2c7230d9aaa78ef84dab92cb94ad0d4f16d2","tid":2026421,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁要確保冇人俾狗告先得喎"},{"pid":"c8d284363dadee995384f6a5d8bfbcec7707cdfc","tid":2026421,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"有得申請法援請好好善用。<br />\n但都要捐，唔通唔打咩。<br />\n如果手足唔打，建議可轉為安家費或創業費？"}]}